CatDescriptText: Headline for related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, January 9, 1954, pg. 17, reads: "Jones Inducted as Councilman"
TitMainTitle: Pittsburgh City Councilman Paul F. Jones and his wife, Antoinette Jones, standing with other men and women in Pittsburgh City Council Chambers with flowers in foreground and Pittsburgh crest on walls at City County Building
